ivardefs.name: contact_
ivardefs.desc: Contact details to assist a user in finding and communicating with the publisher.

ivardefs.name: date

ivardefs.name: description
ivardefs.desc: A free text natural language description of the compartment definition from a consumer's perspective.

ivardefs.name: experimental
ivardefs.desc: A boolean value to indicate that this compartment definition is authored for testing purposes (or education/evaluation/marketing), and is not intended to be used for genuine usage.

ivardefs.name: jurisdiction_
ivardefs.desc: A legal or geographic region in which the compartment definition is intended to be used.

ivardefs.name: name
ivardefs.desc: A natural language name identifying the compartment definition. This name should be usable as an identifier for the module by machine processing applications such as code generation.

ivardefs.name: publisher
ivardefs.desc: The name of the individual or organization that published the compartment definition.

ivardefs.name: purpose
ivardefs.desc: Explaination of why this compartment definition is needed and why it has been designed as it has.

ivardefs.name: resource_
ivardefs.desc: Information about how a resource is related to the compartment.

ivardefs.name: search
ivardefs.desc: Whether the search syntax is supported,.

ivardefs.name: status
ivardefs.desc: The status of this compartment definition. Enables tracking the life-cycle of the content.

ivardefs.name: title
ivardefs.desc: A short, descriptive, user-friendly title for the compartment definition.

ivardefs.name: url

ivardefs.name: useContext_
ivardefs.desc: The content was developed with a focus and intent of supporting the contexts that are listed. These terms may be used to assist with indexing and searching for appropriate compartment definition instances.
